(4, 'How to keep your teeth healthy during Covid-19 outbreak?', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:107%;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Calibri Light&quot;,sans-serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-latin;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ansi-language:EN-IN;\r\nmso-fareast-language:EN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Keeping your teeth and gums\r\nhealthy might not be on front of your mind during this pandemic era, but a new\r\nresearch by the scientists of Japan might change your mind. The researchers believe\r\nthat non-infectious viral acid could be accumulated in uncleansed oral cavities.\r\nThis may lead to a false positive result in Covid testing.</span><br></p>', '<p><img src=\"data:image/jpeg;base64,\" data-filename=\"best dentist in pune.jpg\" style=\"width: 704px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:107%;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Calibri Light&quot;,sans-serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-latin;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ansi-language:EN-IN;\r\nmso-fareast-language:EN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\"><br></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:107%;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Calibri Light&quot;,sans-serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-latin;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ansi-language:EN-IN;\r\nmso-fareast-language:EN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Keeping your teeth and gums\r\nhealthy might not be on front of your mind during this pandemic era, but a new\r\nresearch by the scientists of Japan might change your mind. The researchers believe\r\nthat non-infectious viral acid could be accumulated in uncleansed oral cavities.\r\nThis may lead to a false positive result in Covid testing.</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:\r\n&quot;Calibri Light&quot;,sans-serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">Thus, it can be said that\r\nteeth cleaning and mouth washing removes viral acid in the mouth and improves\r\nthe accuracy of testing.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:\r\n&quot;Calibri Light&quot;,sans-serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">Well if this does not seem\r\nto be reasonable enough for a good oral hygiene routine, it is necessary to\r\nunderstand that your mouth serves as the first line of defence to the rest of\r\nyour body. Mokashi dental clinic is known as one of the </span><a href=\"https://www.mokashidentalclinic.com/dentist-in-wakad.html\" target=\"_blank\">best cosmetic dentistin Pune</a><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:\r\n&quot;Calibri Light&quot;,sans-serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">.</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:\r\n&quot;Calibri Light&quot;,sans-serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:\r\n&quot;Calibri Light&quot;,sans-serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">Now what if your mouth is\r\nnot healthy? Your entire immune system might be weakened in this testing time\r\nwhen it is crucial to fight the virus. So by keeping your mouth healthy, you\r\ncan not only brighten your smile but also boost your immune system.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:\r\n&quot;Calibri Light&quot;,sans-serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">So if you are convinced\r\nenough to keep your mouth healthy now, read on to know various ways to do it:<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><b><i><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Calibri Light&quot;,sans-serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-latin;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calibri Light&quot;;mso-fareast-theme-font:major-latin;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-latin;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-latin\">1.<span style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span></i><!--[endif]--><i><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Calibri Light&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">Eat, Brush, Floss, And Sleep!</span></i><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Calibri Light&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16pt;\">&nbsp;</span></b></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Calibri Light&quot;,sans-serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-latin;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">First\r\nof all wash your hands before any personal dental care. Brushing twice a day\r\nand flossing once a day is mandatory for good oral care. Of course, brushing in\r\nthe morning is an important ritual for us, but that does not mean that night brushing\r\ncan be ignored.</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Calibri Light&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Calibri Light&quot;,sans-serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-latin;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">If you\r\ndonâ€™t brush your teeth at night, you let the plaque grow undisturbed overnight.\r\nSo next time when you feel too exhausted to brush, remember that you are\r\ninviting those nasty bacteria to house on your teeth!</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Calibri Light&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><i><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Calibri Light&quot;,sans-serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-latin;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Calibri Light&quot;;mso-fareast-theme-font:major-latin;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-latin;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-latin\">2.<span style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span></i><!--[endif]--><b><i><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Calibri Light&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">Brush, But Donâ€™t Over brush!</span></i><i style=\"font-size: 1rem;\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Calibri Light&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></i></b></p><p class=\"MsoListParagrap